    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver exceptional induction notes and sharp throttle response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and features refreshed subframe bushings to ensure structural rigidity. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the hydraulic steering rack remains precise and the damping is firm, providing the communicative feedback expected of a well-sorted M-chassis. A purposeful build for the purist who values mechanical pedigree over showroom vanity.",
